## ğŸ–¥ï¸ Frontend Pages (Next.js â†’ Netlify)

- **`/`** â€” Landing: "Describe your product idea" â†’ text input â†’ creates session UUID
- **`/session/[id]`** â€” Streamed chat with PM Agent (Groq SSE)
- **`/session/[id]/report`** â€” Clean PDF-style view of Foundation Doc + Validation Report

***

## ğŸš€ 4-Week Build Sequence

**Week 1 â€” Skeleton**
- Init Next.js, deploy to Netlify, connect Neon DB, test Groq stream + Tavily call

**Week 2 â€” PM Agent (Phase 1)**
- Routeway Conductor routing, PM Agent 8-question loop, save Foundation Doc to Neon, render it on `/report`

**Week 3 â€” Research Agent (Phase 2)**
- Auto-generate Tavily queries from Foundation Doc, Groq summarizes results, save + render Validation Report

**Week 4 â€” Polish + Ship**
- Error handling, mobile responsiveness, session sharing via URL, record demo

